OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FCloudy this
OL,6,Fevening with occasional light rain.
OL,7,FStaying cloudy overnight with more in
OL,8,Fthe way of persistent rain spreading
OL,9,Fsoutheast later in the night.
OL,10,FFreshening southwesterly winds.
OL,11,
OL,12,CWednesday:FCloudy in the morning with
OL,13,Fsome rain. Drier and eventually
OL,14,Fclearer conditions spreading from the
OL,15,Fnorth later in the day.
OL,16,
OL,17,COutlook for Thursday to Saturday:FDry
OL,18,Fwith bright spells on Thursday, chance
OL,19,Fof rain late evening. Unsettled with
OL,20,Fshowers or longer spells of rain on
OL,21,FFriday and Saturday.
